Air Canada Flight Attendants Poised to Strike as Raitt Vows to Bar Walkout

-- B y   W i l l   D a l e y
-- 
2011-10-12T14:59:46Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-12/air-canada-flight-attendants-poised-to-strike-as-raitt-vows-to-bar-walkout.html
Flight attendants represented by the
Canadian Union of Public Employees said they are preparing to
walk off the job at 12:01 a.m. tomorrow, according to a
statement.  The union is in a legal strike position and has received no
order to the contrary, the group said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Will Daley at 
